  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Applied Cooking Url\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/applied-cooking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Check%20out%20my%20other%20mod%20that%20connects%20Applied%20Energistics%202%20and%20Cooking%20for%20Blockheads-Link%20at%20the%20bottom-edbd7e?labelColor=154a48&style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Applied Cooking Promo\" width=\"845\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Refined Cooking Url\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/refined-cooking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Check%20out%20my%20other%20mod%20that%20connects%20Refined%20Storage%20and%20Cooking%20for%20Blockheads-Link%20at%20the%20bottom-e78a4e?labelColor=7f1620&style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Refined Cooking Promo\" width=\"800\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p><a title=\"MelonCube Partner Link\" href=\"https://meloncube.net/sebastrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://www.meloncube.net/partners/custom-banners/f22247d3-fc0d-404f-a8b1-0ad4d5aca331.png\" alt=\"MelonCube Partner Banner\" width=\"900\" height=\"158\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Available%20for%20Forge-1.19%20%7C%201.18-800000?labelColor=FFA500&style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Minecraft Versions Badge\" width=\"266\" height=\"28\" /> <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Install%20on-Client%20&%20Server-800000?labelColor=FFA500&style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"Applied Cooking Install Badge\" width=\"240\" height=\"28\" /></p>\n<h2>Description</h2>\n<p>This is a common lib project for all Sebastrn mods.</p>\n<p>I have plans to provide support for my mods for both Forge and Fabric (right now I only support Forge).</p>\n<p>This library mod will be the starting point for common code I need for all my mods (Utility methods, abstractions, interfaces and so on).</p>\n<p>Also, this mod adds a guidebook (built with Patchouli) for all my mods so players can have some help to get started.</p>\n<p>I don't recommend anybody to build on top of this as I won't provide documentation and will change things radically to suit my mods' needs.</p>\n<h2>Socials</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Sebastrn's Curseforge\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/itssebastrn/projects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=ItsSebastrn&color=800000&labelColor=FFA500&style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Sebastrn's Curseforge\" width=\"148\" height=\"28\" /></a> <a title=\"Sebastrn's Modrinth\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Sebastrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Sebastrn&color=800000&labelColor=FFA500&style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Sebastrn's Modrinth\" width=\"125\" height=\"28\" style=\"max-height: 28px;\" /></a> <a title=\"Sebastrn's Twitter\" href=\"https://twitter.com/ItsSebastrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=@ItsSebastrn&color=800000&labelColor=FFA500&style=for-the-badge&logo=twitter&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Sebastrn's Twitter\" width=\"159\" height=\"28\" /></a> <a title=\"Sebastrn's Youtube\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC46TYUp8WpcFub8NxuGA66A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Sebastrn&color=800000&labelColor=ffa500&style=for-the-badge&logo=youtube&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Sebastrn's Youtube\" width=\"125\" height=\"28\" /></a> <a title=\"Sebastrn's Twitch\" href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/itssebastrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=ItsSebastrn&color=800000&labelC